      "id": "d2_13",
      "text": "For the next questions, the response options are 'Not at all,' 'A Little,' 'Somewhat,' 'Very,' or 'Extremely.' How much do any of these health issues (above) make it harder for you to take care of yourself? (e.g., hygiene, grooming, dressing, eating, housework, living independently, etc.)",
      "type": "single_choice",
      "required": true,
      "breadcrumb": "impact_on_self_care",
      "options": [
        {"value": "1", "label": "Not at all", "score": 1},
        {"value": "2", "label": "A Little", "score": 2},
        {"value": "3", "label": "Somewhat", "score": 3},
        {"value": "4", "label": "Very", "score": 4},
        {"value": "5", "label": "Extremely", "score": 5}
      ]
    },
